 He thought that the trade union movement was   reformism reformist   and even   Conservatism conservative    citing as essentially bourgeois and anti worker the phenomenon of professional union officials  Malatesta warned that the syndicalists aims were in perpetuating syndicalism itself  whereas anarchists must always have anarchy as their end and consequently refrain from committing to any particular method of achieving it 
 
